• There are no reasons to reject the application after all.
Mrs. [redacted_name] has to bring the following to the representation of the Netherlands:
a copie of this letter;
the "form for authorisation for temporary stay", filled out and signed. You can find it on
the website www.nederlandwereldwijd.nl/mvv-verlening-formulier. For the English version visit www.netherlandsworldwide.nl/mvv- issue-form;
Her passport;
a copy of her passport;
a new, never used passport photo. The requirements for the passport photo
can be found at rijksoverheid.nl/eisen-pasfoto;
a copy of (the page with the photo and identity data of) your
passport;
The original marriage certificate;
copies of the original documents mentioned above as well as of the potential
translations and legalisationstamps. The representation of the Netherlands keeps the copy and returns the original.
In consultation with the Immigration and Naturalisation Services, the representation of the Netherlands can always require additional documents.
Fingerprints, signature and passport photo
to create the residency permet the Immigration and Naturalisation Services need the fingerprints, passport photo and signature of Mrs. [redacted_name]. The Immigration and Naturalisation Services can also use this data to establish who she is. The representation of the Netherlands therefore takes her fingerprints. She signs and gives her passport photo.
